{
  "_comment": "Binding layer (DR4/DR6). Maps the ASPEC's abstract mock identifiers to the concrete resource and credential IDs in the target n8n instance. A production deployment would populate this automatically from each platform's resource-listing API; here it is filled by hand so the translation is reproducible. Replace every <YOUR_...> placeholder below with the real IDs/names from your own n8n instance before running.",
